<div class="content line">
<div class="main">
<h2 id="participants">Participants</h2>
<p class="lead">Pat-INFORMED is an initiative of WIPO, the International Federation of Pharmaceutical Manufacturers and Associations (IFPMA) and 20 leading, research-based biopharmaceutical companies.</p>
<p>These 20 companies chose to voluntarily provide information on key patents for their approved pharmaceutical products in therapeutic categories covered by Pat-INFORMED. They also commit to respond to bona fide inquiries from procurement agencies.</p>
<p>WIPO builds on its large database expertise to hosts this data, providing links to Patentscope when possible. Patent data is provided and updated directly by the companies.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/pat-informed/en/participants/">List of participants</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="complementary">
<figure><img src="/export/sites/www/pat-informed/images/ifpma-wipo_500-280.jpg" alt="IFPMA and WIPO logos" />
<figcaption>A public-private partnership between<a href="https://www.wipo.int"> WIPO</a> and the research-based pharmaceutical industry, Pat-INFORMED builds on the strength of each sector to tackle global health challenges.</figcaption>
</figure>
</div>
</div>
